  <title>Styx 0.1.0 released</title>
  <summary type="xhtml">
    <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
      <p>First release of Styx!</p>

<p>Styx is a functional static site generator based on the <a href="http://nixos.org/nix/">Nix package manager</a>.</p>

<p>It is possible to test this release of Styx in a <code>nix-shell</code>:</p>

<pre><code>$ nix-shell -p $(nix-build https://github.com/ericsagnes/styx/archive/0.1.0.tar.gz)
$ styx --help
</code></pre>

<p>Styx can be installed with the <code>nix-env</code> command:</p>

<pre><code>$ nix-env -i $(nix-build https://github.com/ericsagnes/styx/archive/0.1.0.tar.gz)
$ styx --help
</code></pre>

<p>Learn more in the <a href="https://styx-static.github.io/styx-site/documentation-v0-1-0.html">Styx 0.1.0 Documentation</a>.</p>

<p>If you want to contribute to Styx, please join the <a href="https://github.com/styx-static/styx/">GitHub repository</a>.</p>

<p>Bugs should be reported to the <a href="https://github.com/styx-static/styx/issues">issue tracker</a>.</p>

    </div>
